data.description: Nestled on a corner lot this home is right at 2 miles away from I-10 and I-49! Open living, dining, and kitchen area with wood laminate flooring! Galley kitchen with ample countertop space and cabinet storage! Spacious master bedroom with built-in makeup vanity, attached bathroom, and walk-in closet. Three spare bedrooms, a guest bath, and a large laundry room wrap up the interior of this home.  Brick paver patio space! Make this one yours today!
